description.en: Pastebin.com is the number one paste tool since 2002. Pastebin is a website where you can store text online for a set period of time.
description.ga_IE: Is é Pastebin.com an Uimhir Greamaigh Uimhir a hAon ó 2002. Is láithreán gréasáin é Pastebin inar féidir leat téacs a stóráil ar líne ar feadh tréimhse ama.
